irectory.\n\nWait, no - I pushed from the `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, which contains ALL the agent workspaces. The remote `origin` was set to `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`, so ALL of `v4-ecosystem-review` was pushed there.\n\n\nThat's exactly what happened - I pushed the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` directory to GitHub, so Lead is seeing all 34 agent workspaces instead of just the setup folder they needed. The setup-openclaw repo was just a subdirectory within that, not the whole thing."},{"type":"text","text":"Dạ **bị đẩy nhầm toàn bộ workspace lên** — vì em push từ thư mục cha `v4-ecosystem-review/`, không phải chỉ `ahv-openclaw-setup/`.\n\nTrên GitHub giờ chứa **34 workspaces + toàn bộ agent files** — không đúng. Lead cần xóa repo GitHub và tạo lại đúng.\n\n**Cách xử lý:**\n\n1. **Xóa repo** `setup-openclaw` trên GitHub\n2. **Tạo repo mới** trên GitHub\n3. **Xóa remote sai** trên máy:\n```bash\ngit remote remove origin\n```\n4. **Clone lại đúng folder**:\n```bash\n# Trên máy Lead, clone repo mới về\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\ncd setup-openclaw\nnpm install\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js\n```\n\nTrên máy này (atu-ahv-ai006), repo đúng đã có sẵn tại:\n```\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/\n```\n\nLead muốn em xử lý xóa repo trên GitLab/GitHub không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":611,"output":532,"totalTokens":143008,"cacheRead":141433,"cacheWrite":432,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228252270,"responseId":"062e4a9e2e309272db3ce42e0474aacd","__openclaw":{"id":"576f7fad","seq":1731}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thôi —cached đi push lại"}],"timestamp":1776229043249,"__openclaw":{"id":"fcae8735","seq":1732},"senderLabel":"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)"}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provi